1. Make a new directory(folder)
Ans: mkdir file1
Commnet: Directory means Folder.

2.Create text file using touch
Ans: touch test1

3. Delete a single file
Ans: rm file1

4.Change working directory
Ans: cd

5. how to Move to parent folder using cd
Ans: cd ~

6.List contents of a folder including hidden files
Ans: ls -al

7.Print current directory
Ans: pwd

8. How to set hostname
Ans: 
hostnamectl
sudo hostnamectl set-hostname new-hostname
or
sudo nano /etc/hostname
sudo nano /etc/hosts 
sudo reboot 

9. How to set timezone
Ans: timedatectl
sudo timedatectl set-timezone Asia/Dhaka

10. How to move file /tmp
Ans:  mv file1 /tmp
Comment: Also mv use for rename
  
